$ Small test deck for the Nastran .bdf reader (Layer 1).
$ Covers: comments, GRID (small field), CTETRA (volume), CTRIA3/CQUAD4 (shells).
$ Field layout is fixed 8-column small field: 10 fields of 8 chars per line.
$
$23456789012345678901234567890123456789012345678901234567890123456789012345678
BEGIN BULK
$ --- Nodes ---
$GRID    ID      CP      X1      X2      X3
GRID    1               0.0     0.0     0.0
GRID    2               1.0     0.0     0.0
GRID    3               0.0     1.0     0.0
GRID    4               0.0     0.0     1.0
GRID    5               1.0     1.0     0.0
GRID    6               1.0     1.0     1.0
$ --- One tetrahedron (volume element) ---
$CTETRA  EID     PID     G1      G2      G3      G4
CTETRA  10      1       1       2       3       4
$ --- A triangular shell ---
$CTRIA3  EID     PID     G1      G2      G3
CTRIA3  20      1       2       5       3
$ --- A quad shell ---
$CQUAD4  EID     PID     G1      G2      G3      G4
CQUAD4  30      1       2       5       6       3
ENDDATA
